    ...    ELSE IF    ${COMPUTE_3_PACKET_COUNT_AFTER_PING}==${COMPUTE_3_PACKET_COUNT_BEFORE_PING}+${NO_OF_PING_PACKETS}    Run Keywords    Log    Packets forwarded via Compute Node 3
    ...    AND    Verify_Packet_Count    ${OS_COMPUTE_3_IP}    ${IP}
